         <div type="translation">
            <p><choice corresp="#a2 #a3 #a4"><seg><seg type="prim_transl">Even if he has committed an offence by craving, the person will establish to destroy (?) it (= the offence) [and] fear of his life will disappear.</seg><bibl><title corresp="ref:peyrot2013b"/><citedRange>714</citedRange></bibl></seg></choice></p>
         </div>
         <div type="comments">
